{{- define "reviewer-state-transitions" -}}
{{- if eq .Role "code-reviewer"}}

REVIEWER STATE TRANSITIONS:
- REVIEWING_CODE → CODE_APPROVED (code meets requirements, spec, and has tests)
- REVIEWING_CODE → CODE_REJECTED (issues found — provide structured feedback)
{{- else if eq .Role "code-plan-reviewer"}}

CODE PLAN REVIEWER STATE TRANSITIONS:
- REVIEWING_CODING_PLAN → CODING_PLAN_APPROVED
- REVIEWING_CODING_PLAN → CODING_PLAN_REJECTED
{{- else if eq .Role "epic-plan-reviewer"}}

EPIC PLAN REVIEWER STATE TRANSITIONS:
- REVIEWING_EPIC_PLAN → EPIC_PLAN_APPROVED
- REVIEWING_EPIC_PLAN → EPIC_PLAN_REJECTED
{{- else if eq .Role "us-reviewer"}}

US REVIEWER STATE TRANSITIONS:
- REVIEWING_US → US_APPROVED
- REVIEWING_US → US_REJECTED
{{- end}}
{{- end -}}
